	(lib_symbols)
	(text "Yellow\nActivity"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 80.01 265.43 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1 1)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "0c284fc3-43ec-49ca-8d4a-370d64171e07")
	)
	(text "Power Enable Sequencing Network\n\nThe STM32 controls all subsystem power rails via GPIO.\nPower-on sequence (from main.cpp):\n  1. +1V0_FPGA (PE7) - FPGA core\n  2. +1V8_FPGA (PE8) - FPGA aux/bank 34\n  3. +3V3_FPGA (PE9) - FPGA I/O banks\n  4. +1V8_CLOCK (PG4) - AD9523 clock synth\n  5. +3V3_CLOCK (PG5) - ADF4382 LO synth\n  6. +5V0_ADAR (PE10) - ADAR1000 beamformers\n  7. +3V3_ADAR12/34 (PE11/PE12) - ADAR regulators\n  8. +3V3_ADTR (PE13) - ADC/DAC transmitter\n  9. +3V3_SW (PE14) - RF switches\n  10. +5V0_PA1/2/3 (PG0/1/2) - PA stages\n  11. +5V5_PA (PG3) - PA final stage\n\nEach enable drives the EN pin of a regulator/LDO.\n100K pulldown on each EN pin ensures safe default off."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 25.4 49.53 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "12339191-8ece-41fd-aa67-608e25a689b8")
	)
	(text "+3V3 FPGA I/O (PE9)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 58.42 154.94 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1 1)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "14c629c3-cf6a-44f8-a4db-7d463448191e")
	)
	(text "Internal Watchdog (IWDG)\nConfigured in firmware - no external components\nTimeout protects against MCU lockup during PA operation"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 24.13 280.67 0)
		(effects
